        <h1 class="landing-page-heading">{% editable_text title153, hint: "a title", format: raw, rows: 1 %}Beauty & Spa Treatments{% endeditable_text %}</h1>
        <h4>{% editable_text title154, hint: "a title", format: raw, rows: 1 %}Introduction{% endeditable_text %}</h4>
        <p>{% editable_text title155, hint: "a title", format: raw, rows: 1 %}
          In body and beauty therapy, in massage and in clinical therapy, The Hogarth Spa offers a comprehensive range of treatments to relax and restore you. Our committed team of experts is ready to consult with you, to recommend, to resolve.
          {% endeditable_text %}
        </p>
