        </p>

        <h4>{% editable_text title158, hint: "a title", format: raw, rows: 1 %}Contact The Hogarth Beauty Spa{% endeditable_text %}</h4>
        <p>{% editable_text title159, hint: "a title", format: raw, rows: 1 %}
          Telephone 020 8995 4600 to arrange an appointment.{% endeditable_text %}
        </p>

        <h4>{% editable_text title160, hint: "a title", format: raw, rows: 1 %}What if I am late for my appointment?{% endeditable_text %}</h4>
        <p>{% editable_text title161, hint: "a title", format: raw, rows: 1 %}
        Arriving late will simply reduce the time for your treatment, potentially reducing its effectiveness and your pleasure. Your treatment will end on time so that our next client is not delayed.{% endeditable_text %}
        </p>

        <h4>{% editable_text title162, hint: "a title", format: raw, rows: 1 %}Cancellation Policy{% endeditable_text %}</h4>
        <p>{% editable_text title163, hint: "a title", format: raw, rows: 1 %}
          Clients who do not cancel treatments 24 hours in advance of the scheduled appointment time will be charged the full amount. We would still appreciate a call so that we can offer the appointment to another client.{% endeditable_text %}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

        
